<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lid" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lid,</orth> the membrane that covers the eye, the eyelid: <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.266" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 266</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.121" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 121</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.3.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 3, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.2.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 2, 20</bibl>. <cit><quote>by God's l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.228" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 228</bibl></cit> (Pandarus' oath).
